%% UI automation topology for FieldWorks
%% Render with: mmdc -i ui-automation-topology.mmd -o ui-automation-topology.svg
flowchart TD
    A[build.ps1 -BuildTests] --> B[Output/Debug/FieldWorks.exe]
    A --> C[FieldWorksUiAutomationTests.dll]

    subgraph TestHarness [Test harness inside execution environment]
        C --> D[FwUiTestBase]
        D --> E[Temp project root]
        D --> F[Temp settings root]
        D --> G[Process env overrides]

        E --> H[TestLangProj copy]
        F --> I[Seeded update/reporting settings]
        G --> J[FEEDBACK=false, AssertUiEnabled=false]

        D --> K[Launch FieldWorks.exe -db TestLangProj]
        K --> L[FlaUI automation backend]
        L --> M[Main window + shell navigation]
        M --> N[Screenshots + step diagnostics]
    end

    subgraph CIPath [CI: direct desktop]
        O[ui-tests.yml] --> A
        O --> P[testui.ps1 -Mode DirectDesktop]
        P --> C
        P --> Q1[TRX artifacts]
    end

    subgraph LocalPath [Local: warm Sandbox default]
        S[Local developer] --> T[testui.ps1 default Sandbox mode]
        T --> U[Warm Windows Sandbox]
        U -->|Output/Debug mapped read-only| B
        U --> C
        U -->|write results| V[Mapped writable results folder]
        V --> W[_status.json + _done sentinel]
        T -->|poll status file| W
        W --> Q2[TRX + PNG artifacts on host]
    end

    N --> R[PNG artifacts]